rice-smart-specs</id><author><name>托马斯·瑞克</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-09-14T05:22:03-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-14T05:22:03-04:00</updated><title> iFixit 现已提供 Google Pixel 平板电脑零件和维修指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;某人拆除 Google Pixel 平板电脑电池的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/35K0oQoM_R4NpfkD9NHYjWZsh3k=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72645737/Google_Pixel_Tablet_iFixit.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Pixel 平板电脑用户现在可以更轻松地更换设备的电池、屏幕和其他组件。&lt;/em>; |图片：iFixit&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;jJodaT&quot;>;现在对于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23765921/google-pixel-tablet-review&quot;>;Google 来说更容易了感谢 Google 与维修权冠军 iFixit 之间的合作，Pixel 平板电脑&lt;/a>;用户可以维修自己的设备。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5google.com/2023/09/14/pixel-tablet-repair-parts-ifixit/&quot;>;&lt;em>;9to5Google&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 发现，&lt;a href =&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifixit.com%2FParts%2FGoogle_Pixel_Tablet&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A% 2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F9%2F14%2F23873136%2Fgoogle-pixel-tablet-ifixit-parts-self-repair-guides&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;正品 Pixel 平板电脑部件&lt; /a>; 现在可以在 iFixit 网站上购买，还有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifixit.com% 2FDevice%2FGoogle_Pixel_Tablet%23Section_Replacement&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F9%2F14%2F23873136%2Fgoogle-pixel-tablet-ifixit-parts-self-repair-guides“ rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;用户维修指南&lt;/a>;，引导您完成如何安装各种组件。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;giBLlD&quot;>;A &lt;a href=&quot;https: //go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifixit.com%2Fproducts%2Fgoogle-pixel-tablet-rear-case-genuine&amp;amp;referrer